column2: Electrophysiology: Experience in the investigation and management of invasive and non-invasive electrophysiology and cardiac devices.
Atrial fibrillation ablation: Experience in point by point WACA with Carto and Ensite 3D mapping systems, as well as pulmonary vein cryo-ablation.
Diagnosis (both non-invasive and invasive) and ablation of supraventricular arrhythmias, including (macro-reentrant and focal) atrial tachycardias.
Ventricular tachycardia ablation: Experience in PVC ablation and VT ablation in ischemic and non-ischemic heart disease.

Cardiac devices implantation: Experience in the implantation and programming of implantable loop recorder, pacemaker, ICD, and CRT-P/D devices, as well as implantation of Boston Scientific subcutaneous ICD.
Clinical: Experience in Cardiology and Internal Medicine.

Scientific research: Experience in the field of basic mechanisms of cardiac arrhythmias: electrophysiology, electrocardiography, echocardiography, cardiac microsurgery on rodents, molecular research techniques (protein analysis, immunohistochemistry, PCR techniques, etc).

Education: Experience in academic teaching in the field of Cardiovascular Physiology (biomedical sciences and medical students).","{'country': 'Netherlands', 'short': 'Arnhem-Nijmegen Region', 'city': None, 'state': None, 'default': 'Arnhem-Nijmegen Region'}",True,False,[],"{'primary_locale': {'country': 'US', 'language': 'en'}, 'supported_locales': [{'country': 'US', 'language': 'en'}], 'profile_languages': [{'name': 'Arabic', 'proficiency': 'NATIVE_OR_BILINGUAL'}, {'name': 'Berber languages (Tamazight)', 'proficiency': 'NATIVE_OR_BILINGUAL'}, {'name': 'Dutch', 'proficiency': 'NATIVE_OR_BILINGUAL'}, {'name': 'English', 'proficiency': 'NATIVE_OR_BILINGUAL'}, {'name': 'French', 'proficiency': 'LIMITED_WORKING'}, {'name': 'German', 'proficiency': 'LIMITED_WORKING'}, {'name': 'Moroccan', 'proficiency': 'NATIVE_OR_BILINGUAL'}, {'name': 'Persian', 'proficiency': 'ELEMENTARY'}, {'name': 'Spanish', 'proficiency': 'ELEMENTARY'}, {'name': 'Turkish', 'proficiency': 'ELEMENTARY'}]}",Hospital & Health Care,"[{'date': {'start': {'month': None, 'day': None, 'year': 2004}, 'end': {'month': None, 'day': None, 'year': 2008}}, 'school': {'name': 'Utrecht University', 'logo': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/C510BAQG6HfmPTdJKXw/company-logo_400_400/0/1519884681258?e=1700092800&v=beta&t=QmNHoENF2Y_jlRACSsZ9TEtxi26_FphbWXhv1lZ3mrE', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/school/universiteit-utrecht/'}, 'degree_name': 'Doctor of Philosophy (Ph.D.)', 'field_of_study': '""Arrhythmogenesis in the remodeled heart.
